      "comment": "NO MORE EXTRAS (6) had the drop on the lead from the rails draw last start but could only manage second, beaten 1.3 lengths (26.31) at Geelong in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 460m. The form from his last run stacks up well. Key chance in this line up. SIT AND STEER (1) finished third (30.34) two back at Sandown but out of the placings last time when 6th at The Meadows. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Should be about the money. FOXY ROXY (2) is a smart beginner who has shown good improvement at her last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 2nd at this track over 450m. Will give a great sight again. BASEMENT (4) will need to repeat last run to feature.",
